TreePackage

Interface BinaryTreeAccessInterface<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryTreeInterface<T>, TreeInterface<T>, TreeIteratorInterface<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BinaryWithParentsTreeAccessInterface<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryTreeWithAccess

    public interface BinaryTreeAccessInterface<T>
extends BinaryTreeInterface<T>
    This interface is similar to the DecisionTreeInterface from Chapter 23 and allows a client to move down from the root in a binary tree.
